                                <h2 class="text-center mt-0">Leggo Manzoni/Wo-Dú Manzoni. Reading <i>The Betrothed</i>
                                    in Beijing</h2>
                                <p>
                                    <strong>March 13–25, 2025</strong>. From March 13 to 25, 2025, the <i>Leggo Manzoni</i>
                                    project will be presented at Peking University, as part of the initiative: <strong>Leggo
                                        Manzoni/Wo-Dú Manzoni. Reading <i>The Betrothed</i> in Beijing</strong>, which
                                    aims to develop a series of educational collaborations between the University of
                                    Bologna (Prof. Paola Italia), the University of Parma (Prof. Giulia Raboni), the
                                    degree course in <i>Italian Language and Literature</i>, and the <i>Digital
                                        Humanities</i> center at Peking University, coordinated by Prof. Silvano Mo
                                    Cheng.
                                    The project, developed under the patronage of the 
                                        <a href="https://www.casadelmanzoni.it/il-centro-nazionale-di-studi-manzoniani"
                                        target="_blank">National Center for Manzonian Studies</a>,
                                    in collaboration with the <a href="https://iicpechino.esteri.it/it/"
                                        target="_blank">Italian Cultural Institute</a> in Beijing and the
                                        <a href="https://www.treccani.it/fondazione/" target="_blank">Treccani
                                        Foundation</a>, will run from 2025 to 2026,
                                    and will involve – through an innovative peer-to-peer teaching method – students
                                    from the University of Bologna as teaching tutors and students from Peking
                                    University.
                                </p>
                                <p>To learn more <a href="./pekino">visit the dedicated page</a> or
                                        <a href="https://magazine.unibo.it/archivio/2025/01/15/leggere-i-promessi-sposi-a-pechino"
                                        target="_blank">read the article on UniBo Magazine</a>.</p>
                                <hr class="divider">
                                </hr>
                                <h2 class="text-center mt-0">"Bringing Manzoni to China" – Corriere di Bologna</h2>
                                <p>
