                                    entitled "Bringing Manzoni to China" describing the Unibo project "Leggo
                                    Manzoni/Wo-Dú Manzoni" led by Prof. Paola Italia. The article, written by Massimo
                                    Marino, describes the initiative that will make <i>The Betrothed</i> available in
                                    Chinese, through the collaboration between the University of Bologna, the University
                                    of Parma and Peking University with Prof. Silvano Mo Cheng.
